    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.91 / v2 + 0.91)) - (wp.exp(tmp + 0.79) * (v1 + 0.98 / v1 + 0.36)))
    v1 = wp.exp(0.52)
    v1 = 0.32
    v0 = tmp
    v2 = wp.cos(v2)
    data[tid] = v0
